Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限的時間將跳動停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們悄聲無息地燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界已經脫軌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被紅世之火所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------OP-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:22.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}高鳴る鼓動　触れあう今世選んで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:29.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}進め　時の果てへ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:35.33,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ぽつり虚空の夜につぶやいた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:41.82,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「また明日ね」って言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:48.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}燃え巡り照らす太陽のような
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:54.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}強さと永遠に焦がれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:01:01.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}たったひとつ残せるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:08.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}存在を抱いた　この瞬間の笑顔を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:16.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ただひとつ守るべきは　君の未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:23.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}刹那  揺れて軋むこの世を選んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:30.36,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと運命の地を翔る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:36.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芽生え始めた炎　胸に秘め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:44.45,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}今世を　来世を　君へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:22.15,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}心潮湧動  循著切身之現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:29.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向時間盡頭出發
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:35.33,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在靜默虛空的夜晚獨自言語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:41.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明天還要再見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:48.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如同炙熱燃燒的太陽般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:54.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}強大得永遠灼燒著自我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:01:01.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果只能留下唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:08.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我只想要你抱緊我  這瞬間的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:16.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}唯一值得守護的  只有你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:23.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}剎那  我選擇了這搖搖欲墜的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:30.36,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}永遠翱翔於那命運之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:36.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}內心偷偷萌生出的  這微弱火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:44.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}無論現在還是未來  飛往你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:23:00.43,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}目を閉じて　感じる鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:05.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もがいてる霧の中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:12.42,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自分の場所　探している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:16.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}闇雲に今日もずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:25.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}痛みのない世界なんてないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:36.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ触れたい　守りたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:46.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}紅く染まる夕暮れを　見つめる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:50.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Just look how beautiful is world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:24:01.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}この出会いで　違う自分見つけたから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:15.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい明日を迎えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:23:00.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}閉上雙眼  感受心的跳動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:05.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在霧中掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:12.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}找尋著自我的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:16.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如今仍然迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:25.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒有苦痛的世界並不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:36.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只想觸碰  守護而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:46.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凝望被染紅的黃昏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:50.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這個世界是多麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:24:01.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因為在這場邂逅中  找到了不一樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:15.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}迎接新的明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:55.04,Optitle,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(315,240)}破碎的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界真正的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這單片眼鏡借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稱為「坂井悠二」的人類究竟是不是火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請自己去確認吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為要現在你來協助我們看來是沒可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像小姐這樣在這個城市土生土長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保留著這個城市純粹的印象的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才適合進行調律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學是火炬的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學沒事的…一定沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在明天的祭典上一定要對坂井同學說「我喜歡你」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把目標放在悠二身上的「化裝舞會」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混進這城市裡的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡原本已經不平衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會變得更糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不能再待在這城市裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算沒有「化裝舞會」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也已經不是人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天必須和母親以及大家分別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想暫時在這裡…和平時一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天穿上和服讓悠二大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後一起去祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了離開這裡的時候也…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起離開這城市？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈  這還真是謎得徹底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們  應該明白這意味著什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的目標就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能使用這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就帶我們走是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試試看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是不是繞著圈子叫我們別跟去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換作平時的你不就一頓臭揍了結的嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣看來明天會下酒雨囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  祭典穿不穿和服去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因為買新的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說要離開這城市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是…害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天5點在橋那裡碰頭怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那小姑娘如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫坂井悠二的男人不是火炬便好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  能冷靜到可以幫忙的程度就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調律這城市稍微有點麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實  歪曲得異常嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在這附近也打上印記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再打一兩個應該夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過  不光是歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有某些不協和感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止可謂是一帆風順
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米諾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離準備完成還剩6小時14分32秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和想的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這花紋非常合適
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看見這麼漂亮的小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠真得會嚇一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小悠好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然已經有離開城市的心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻很痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已經那麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠怎麼搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期六一直是下午開始鍛煉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會早回來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他說過今天晚上開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去祭典的事沒告訴過他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是閒逛去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閒逛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去找小悠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和池他們在緣日玩也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}緣日：參拜神佛的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下便條的話就算錯過也不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡遇見的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠會更吃驚也說不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜  看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蘋果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠緣日來的話絕對會買的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃吃看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要妨礙我們訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是來祭典玩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人說要出門的話就乖乖跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且啊  再那樣繼續的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會做出一道難看的活「人」刺身囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榮太  去買點酒來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒方  走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店還真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有蘋果糖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想知道…坂井同學到底有沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…這樣下去就…永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  剩下的就是等待那位小姐的協助了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  仍然很介意這不協和感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是歪曲太厲害的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有紅世之徒的氣息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前為止還沒有辦法對付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類還真好用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連一個火霧戰士都沒察覺到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授  準備完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就對坂井同學好好說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我喜歡你」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來都沒任何氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草  我想起還有件事要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是紅世之徒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但放出了自在式卻沒有氣息是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概藏在什麼地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  放鬆心情就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  我們去玻璃壇就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要查出紅世之徒的位置就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全給看穿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用法已經知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  不是真打算帶他們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是臨時應急用用罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平時一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說也需要用玻璃壇來調查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這自在式還真大手筆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,設下這麼大的機關  看來不是普通人物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二也一定察覺到了  到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是紅世之徒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先要通知夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田…同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人…坂井同學…騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田一美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼吉田一美會和悠二在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吉田同學知道了我是火炬的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快去追她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事…別去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧  紅世之徒開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須對吉田同學解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二一定要和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要對吉田一美那種人解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們無關的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無關？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和吉田一美毫無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼都沒所謂啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到夏娜會說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說並不是無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「儀裝之驅手」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好久不見了呢  「天壤劫火」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也被這自在式…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬爾克希亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總對這亂七八糟的自在式有不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…「探耽求究」——丹塔里奧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是那個神經病教授沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那傢伙的氣息完全感覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來更加需要玻璃壇了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊一點吧  啟作  榮太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中那傢伙跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走散了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小緒什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了  我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不說給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才和你在一起的女人的事就不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了只是認識而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:17:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是說這的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在矇混了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…小緒  我可要生氣囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然說這種話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  我趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我介意啊…非常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說到底為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為喜歡田中榮太！所以才介意呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意見嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學是…火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學  到底誰把這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅世之徒的攻擊可已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  繼續剛才的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這自在式使得歪曲更厲害了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市將會被嚴重到不能修復的歪曲給吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底為了什麼而這麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有對策嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  只要開始調律就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必要的印記已經打完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需一位能將城市正常姿態印象化的協助者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  實際上已經有心目中的人選了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微出了點紕漏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫作吉田一美的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  她身上帶著的氣息原來是你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她來的話調律馬上就能開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為火霧戰士的使命會好好完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該是火霧戰士們來搗亂的時候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米諾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  開始著手第二作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封絕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法馬上給你答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  待會會來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在封絕中還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  必須做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能辦到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…緣？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤  來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  熱鬧起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後會變成什麼樣還真令人期待啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.89,0:24:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在仍舊無法捕捉到教授的行蹤之際
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「混沌的聖廟」正在御崎市上空逐漸完成
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.19,0:24:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜作為火霧戰士而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.59,0:24:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺著逐漸遠去悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  在戰鬥之中
